+++
date = "2011-08-25"
title = "Russian Sign Language Pronouns, Indexicality and the Signing Space"
host = "The World of Reflexives, Utrecht University"
publishdate = "2011-11-30"

+++

(with Vadim Kimmelman)

In this talk we present a detailed description of the behaviour of various classes of (anaphoric) pronouns in three dialects of the Russian Sign Language. 


**Keywords:** syntax, semantics, binding theory, Russian Sign Language

This is a  talk at the [World of Reflexives](http://languagelink.hum.uu.nl/anatyp/wiki/doku.php?id=program_wor) workshop  at [Utrecht University](http://uu.nl/).


